c: 25
v: 50
t: "wlqd 'anzalna almatar ealaa 'ard dun akhra; lydhkr aladhin 'anzalna ealayhim almatar niemat allah elyhm, fyshkru lh, waliadhakar aladhin muneu mnh, fysareu baltwbt 'iilaa allah - jl wela- lyrhmhm wysqyhm, fa'abaa 'akthar alnaas 'iilaa jhwdana lnemna elyhm, kqwlhm: mtrna bnaw' kadha wkdha"